x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mitski.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mitski.-Credit-Ebru-Yildiz-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/mitski">米茨基</a>宣布为她即将推出的唱片《The Land Is Inhospitable And So Are We》举办聆听派对，并举办电影放映活动。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mitski-laurel-hell-review-3151004">Mitski – 《Laurel Hell》专辑评论：创作的元思考</a></strong></li></ul><p>音乐和电影双重功能将于下周 9 月 7 日星期四上演。这些活动将在八个国际城市的电影院放映，包括芝加哥、达拉斯、伦敦、洛杉矶、墨尔本、纳什维尔、悉尼和纽约 - 另外日本东京的一个天文馆 — 与 Spotify 联合举办的美国活动。</p><p>粉丝们将能够在亲密的环境中聚集在一起，提前预览《土地不适宜居住，我们也是如此》的全部内容。聆听活动结束后，粉丝们将能够观看米茨基精心挑选的电影的放映。入选的电影有泰伦斯·马利克的<em>《天堂之日》</em> 、唐娜·戴奇的<em>《沙漠之心》</em> 、格斯·范·桑特的<em>《药店牛仔》</em>和费德里科·费里尼的<em>《拉斯特拉达》。</em></p><p>日本的活动将于 9 月在涩谷宇宙天文馆举行，届时将在与会者聆听专辑时投射夜空。</p><p>与会者将收到专门为该系列制作的限量版海报。值得注意的是，米茨基本人不会出席。 《土地不适宜居住，我们也是如此》将于 9 月 15 日通过 Dead Oceans 发行。</p><p><a href="https://mitski.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>获取门票和更多信息，并查看以下地点。 </p><figure id="attachment_3491105" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3491105" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3491105" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art.jpg" alt="“土地是好客的”专辑艺术。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Land-Is-In-hospitable-Album-Art-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3491105" class="wp-caption-text"> “土地是好客的”专辑艺术。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><b>“土地不适宜居住，我们也是如此”音乐和电影双重功能</b><b>早期专辑聆听与电影搭配由米茨基选择的日期是：</b></p><p> <strong>2023 年 9 月 7 日</strong><br /><strong>伊利诺伊州芝加哥，戴维斯剧院 [<i>药店牛仔</i>]</strong><br /><strong>达拉斯，德克萨斯州，德克萨斯剧院 [ <i>La Strada</i> ]</strong><br /><strong>加利福尼亚州洛杉矶，脑死亡工作室费尔法克斯 [ <i>Days of Heaven</i> ]</strong><br /><strong>田纳西州纳什维尔，贝尔考特剧院 [<i>药店牛仔</i>]</strong><br /><strong>纽约，纽约，东村，Angelika [<i>沙漠之心</i>]</strong><br /><strong>英国伦敦，绿色的普通屏幕 [<i>沙漠之心</i>]</strong><br /><strong>澳大利亚悉尼，丽兹电影院 [ <i>Days of Heaven</i> ]</strong><br /><strong>澳大利亚墨尔本，丽都电影院 [ <i>Days of Heaven</i> ]</strong></p><p> <strong>2023 年 9 月 14 日</strong><br /><strong>东京天文馆专辑聆听体验、涩谷宇宙天文馆</strong></p><p>上周，米茨基<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mitski-shares-two-new-songs-and-announces-intimate-uk-and-european-shows-3487559">发行了两首新歌《Star》和《Heaven》，并宣布将在英国和欧洲举办一系列亲密演出</a>。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，“星星”和“天堂”最初是多年前构思的，在最终版本发布之前经过反复修改。</p><p>她还宣布，她将于 10 月份在英国和欧洲举行的一系列亲密演出中对《The Land Is Inhospitable And So Are We》中的歌曲进行声学处理。</p><p>巡演预售将于 9 月 7 日开始，次日开始正式发售。<a href="https://mitski.com/pages/tour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">预购《土地荒凉，我们亦如此》的</a>观众可保证预售。</p><p>米茨基的上一张专辑《Laurel Hell》被<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-50-best-albums-of-2022-3363070"><em>《NME</em> 》评为 2022 年最佳专辑第 21 名</a>，Rhian Daly 称赞米茨基“将她与地位的关系放在显微镜下，巧妙地分析了艺术和自我价值与“为刀工作”中名义工具的锋利度”。</p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mitski-announces-listening-parties-for-her-new-album-along-with-film-screenings-3491100">米茨基宣布为她的新专辑举办聆听派对以及电影放映的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Royal Blood 的 Mike Kerr：“与 Josh Homme 的合作让我为这张专辑做好了准备” https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-mike-kerr-interview-josh-homme-back-to-the-water-below-3490995?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=royal-blood-迈克·克尔采访乔什·霍姆回到水下Andrew TrendellWed, 30 Aug 2023 16:12:31 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3490995 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Royal Blood 乐队的 Mike Kerr 在 2023 年 Y Not Festival 上表演（摄影：Luke Brennan/Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位主唱还向《NME》谈到了如何克服“冒名顶替综合症”，并在《Back To The Water Below》中走出自己的舒适区。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-mike-kerr-interview-josh-homme-back-to-the-water-below-3490995">《Royal Blood》的 Mike Kerr 的帖子：“与 Josh Homme 合作为我这张唱片做好了准备”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Royal Blood 乐队的 Mike Kerr 在 2023 年 Y Not Festival 上表演（摄影：Luke Brennan/Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/royal-blood">Royal Blood</a>主唱 Mike Kerr 向<em>NME</em>讲述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/QUEENS-OF-THE-STONE-AGE">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>的 Josh Homme 给予他的信任，以及这如何帮助塑造他们的新专辑《Back To The Water Below》。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-interview-radio-one-big-weekend-muse-support-brighton-homecoming-3474725"><strong>阅读更多：</strong>皇家血统：“这些天每次你张开嘴，你就在掷骰子”</a></li></ul><p>布莱顿摇滚二人组将于明天（9 月 1 日）在伦敦卡姆登电动宴会厅举行亲密的发布会后，于本周五（9 月 1 日）发行他们“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-interview-mountains-midnight-back-to-water-below-jack-white-muse-3448097">本能”的第四张专辑《Back To The Water Below》</a> 。</p><p>虽然这张唱片是由 Kerr 和鼓手 Ben Thatcher 自行制作的，但上一张专辑《Typhoons》是由 Paul Epworth 和 Homme 共同制作的。在接受<em>NME</em>采访时，Kerr 谈到了如何与 Homme 合作，特别是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/josh-homme-desert-sessions-vol-11-12-review-2560576">Homme 2019 年副项目“The Desert Sessions Vol 11/12</a> ”中收录的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-josh-homme-boilermaker-typhoons-producer-kid-having-fun-2922367">上一张专辑单曲“Boilermaker</a> ”中，以及 QOTSA 主唱的建议帮助他整理了新材料。</p><p> “乔什·霍姆 (Josh Homme) 说过，‘如果你对音乐抱有任何期待，那你的期望就太多了’，”科尔说道。 “明天永远是无法保证的，我很惊讶我们已经走到了这一步，而且仍然能够做到这一点。</p><p> “我们从未有过<em>在这个</em>场地演出或进行<em>巡演</em>的野心。我们现在唯一的抱负就是继续创造性地挖掘和推进。它增加燃料。每张唱片结束时我都会想，‘我再也不想这样做了——我崩溃了，我完蛋了’。我不知道如何开始另一张专辑，但当你发现新事物时，所有灵感都会回来。</p><p>克尔继续说道：“制作一张专辑真的很困难。我在[我们的工作室]度过了美妙的时刻，但它们真的转瞬即逝。我大部分时间都在怀疑自己是否能做到这一点。这是冒名顶替综合症——大多数时候认为自己很糟糕。然后你就会想到“也许我并不完全是狗屎”。当你到达终点时，就像跑完一场马拉松一样。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="皇家血统 - 锅炉工（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FoDNFsQGDjE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当被问及他是否曾与撒切尔夫人以外的任何其他音乐家合作或组建另一支乐队时，克尔回答说：“这可能会改变，但我们两个人都从中得到了真正的乐趣。我发现当有其他人在场时很难保持这种活力。我们有更多的乐趣。当我们即兴演奏时，你可能会做任何事。没有权威，也没有成年人。我在与他人合作方面的经历主要是负面的。</p><p> “Josh Homme 对我来说是最出色的，它令人惊叹且非常强大。我对自己和我们正在做的事情有了很多了解。那是一个了不起的时刻。它使我能够完成我们在这张唱片上所做的事情。它给人一种惊人的自信，而且这种自信并没有真正动摇。”</p><p>在谈到制作个人唱片的机会时，克尔告诉我们：“我考虑过这一点，但即使我做了一张个人唱片，我也会说，‘我需要一些鼓’，最终结果就是这样。老实说，我喜欢加入这个乐队，也喜欢 Ben 的支持。我不知道有人如何独自做到这一点。” </p><figure id="attachment_3491072" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3491072" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3491072" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2.jpg" alt="Royal Blood 乐队的迈克·克尔 (Mike Kerr) 和本·撒切尔 (Ben Thatcher) 在 2023 年 Y Not Festival 上表演（摄影：Luke Brennan/Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/royal_blood_mike_kerr_2023_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3491072" class="wp-caption-text"> Royal Blood 乐队的迈克·克尔 (Mike Kerr) 和本·撒切尔 (Ben Thatcher) 在 2023 年 Y Not Festival 上表演（摄影：Luke Brennan/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>展望《Back To The Water Below》，克尔解释了这张专辑的重点是“歌曲创作”。</p><p> “我第一次觉得你可以在钢琴或原声吉他上演奏每一首歌曲，并且这些歌曲将以不同的方式呈现。”他说。 “以前在其他唱片中，有些歌曲是由即兴重复段、肌肉或沉重或响亮的力量引导的。这张唱片就是关于<em>歌曲的，</em>从一开始就是这样。总是让人烦恼的一件事是一首朗朗上口的摇滚歌曲。他们会说，“你怎么敢尝试戴着吉他写一首流行歌曲？”对我们来说，这始终是重点——制造让你难以忘怀的东西。”</p><p>他继续说道：“如果你在一支摇滚乐队中，带着法兹踏板和扩音器出去，却无话可说，背后没有歌曲，那你就是个白痴！你是个装腔作势的人。我们把歌曲创作放在最前面，这让我们有一个框架来把东西放在下面。 </p><figure id="attachment_3468333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3468333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3468333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard.jpg" alt="皇室血统。图片来源：汤姆·比尔德" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Royal-Blood.-Credit-Tom-Beard-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3468333" class="wp-caption-text">皇室血统。图片来源：汤姆·比尔德</figcaption></figure><p>克尔指出新专辑曲目“The Firing Line”对于乐队来说是一个“强大的时刻”，也是他们走出舒适区的突破。</p><p> “我记得《台风》刚刚上映，我并不是在为《皇家血统》写作，”科尔回忆道。 “我有一个奇怪的八弦贝斯，只是在玩。我在大约一个小时内为它制作了整个乐器。</p><p> “这只是为了这样做。我想，‘我他妈的该拿这个做什么呢？’感到有点害怕是做事的好方法。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DAVID-BOWIE">鲍伊</a>有这样的比喻：“总是比你觉得自己能进入的水更深一点”。那就是我们应该存在的地方，所以我们追求它。</p><p> “有趣的是，我们的第一步是不安全的，将其皇家之血化——而我们他妈的摧毁了它。这提醒人们，歌曲才是主导，如果你否认它们应该是什么，那么这是非常明显的。又回到了这首细腻通透、没有任何失真的歌曲小样。对我来说，这样的时刻让我对未来充满希望。我不想继续做同样的事情——我想看看接下来会发生什么。”</p><p>这位主唱补充道：“同时，我也不想疏远我们的粉丝或我自己。这就像试穿衣服一样——你穿上一件夹克，你马上就知道了。你只能欺骗自己这么久。”</p><p> “有时乐队会进行风格调整，比如‘看看我们能做的所有这些事情’。有些乐队来自真实的地方，这很棒，但我不想觉得我们需要这样做。就像，“看看这张该死的放克唱片！”这些歌曲把我们带到了这个地方，而不是我们说，‘让我们做一些我们不太擅长的事情吧！’” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Royal Blood - Pull Me Through（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O86BYcAHuD4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Noting other “surprising” moments in the making of the album, Kerr spoke of how the song &#39;Waves&#39; came from a more “pure” and “vulnerable” place.</p><p> “I knew the album wasn&#39;t done – there was something missing,” said Kerr. “We had a week to decide if we were going to delay the whole thing. I was sat at the piano thinking, &#39;I&#39;m pretty scared writing this&#39;. I was terrified to play Ben the first demo. I felt embarrassed because it was a brand new place to be in with no wall of sound.</p><p> He went on: “I sent Ben a rough sketch of what I was thinking and he was like, &#39;10/10 – we have to do this!&#39; He&#39;s amazing in that he&#39;s so supportive in me trying new things. We had that on the last record with &#39;All We Have Is Now&#39;. I thought, &#39;Is this a bit lame?&#39; There&#39;s an insecure part of me that wants to go out with my chest puffed out and be a pro-wrestler. That&#39;s a part of me and I have fun with it, but it&#39;s not all of me. With songs like &#39;Waves&#39;, there&#39;s a softer side to me that&#39;s never represented on stage, but all my friends know it&#39;s there.</p><p> “It feels important, and it feels good.”</p><p> Next year also marks 10 years since the band released their <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-royal-blood-15546-304468">debut Number One self-titled album</a> .</p><p> Asked if fans can expect an anniversary tour, Kerr replied: “It would be great to mark it by doing some kind of play-through honouring it, but I don&#39;t think about it. It would be great to get back in the van and re-do the original tour. That would be funny.”</p><p> And how about perhaps stepping up to headline Reading &amp; Leeds festival next year?</p><p> “That would be amazing,” replied Kerr. “I&#39;m hoping we can ramp it up. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Royal Blood - Mountains at Midnight (Official Video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ak-xJYNWfzE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Last month, the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-interview-radio-one-big-weekend-muse-support-brighton-homecoming-3474725">band also spoke to <em>NME</em> about the fall-out of their appearance at BBC Radio One&#39;s Big Weekend</a> , as well as lessons learned from touring with Muse.</p><p> Royal Blood release &#39;Back To The Water Below&#39; on September 1, before a run of intimate album launch shows and later a full North America and UK headline tour. <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Froyal-blood-tickets%2Fartist%2F1536591" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> for tickets and more information.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/royal-blood-mike-kerr-interview-josh-homme-back-to-the-water-below-3490995">Royal Blood&#39;s Mike Kerr: “Working with Josh Homme equipped me for this record”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 U2 announce 'Zoo Station' immersive fan experience ahead of Sphere shows https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-announce-zoo-station-immersive-fan-experience-ahead-of-sphere-shows-3491076?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=u2-announce-zoo-station-immersive-fan-experience-ahead-of-sphere-showsLiberty Dunworth Wed, 30 Aug 2023 16:07:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3491076 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="U2 Las Vegas &#039;Zoo Station&#039; hub" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> It features interactive experiences, a TV cinema, limited edition merchandise and more</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-announce-zoo-station-immersive-fan-experience-ahead-of-sphere-shows-3491076">U2 announce &#39;Zoo Station&#39; immersive fan experience ahead of Sphere shows</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="U2 Las Vegas &#039;Zoo Station&#039; hub" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-sphere@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a> have announced &#39;Zoo Station&#39; – an immersive experience for fans, designed ahead of their <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-announce-dates-for-achtung-baby-live-at-sphere-3434889">upcoming Sphere shows</a> .</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/reviews/film-reviews/kiss-the-future-review-u2-bono-3406149">&#39;Kiss The Future&#39; review: remembering U2&#39;s historic gig in war-torn Sarajevo</a></strong></li></ul><p> Opening on September 28, the immersive fan portal, called &#39;Zoo Station: A U2:UV Experience&#39; is designed to help fans gather a deeper understanding of the band&#39;s acclaimed album &#39;Achtung Baby&#39;.</p><p> Aiming to provide “a unique opportunity to interact with U2&#39;s rich artistic legacy”, &#39;Zoo Station&#39; is developed by Vibee, a Live Nation-founded destination experience company and VIP package provider, and is set to be the “ultimate hub for fans”.</p><p> A ​​&#39;Zoo TV Cinema&#39; is featured within the experience, which has been curated by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-edge">The Edge</a> , as well as an Anton Corbijn Gallery, limited edition merchandise, VIP lounges and much more. </p><figure id="attachment_3491084" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3491084" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3491084" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270.jpg" alt="U2 Las Vegas 'Zoo Station' hub" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/u2-las-vegas-hub@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3491084" class="wp-caption-text"> U2 Las Vegas &#39;Zoo Station&#39; hub.图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>It was developed in collaboration with Gavin Friday, U2&#39;s longtime Creative Director, and also had direct input from the band members. The final result spans 12,000 square feet of interactive exhibit space across two floors, and is located within The Venetian Resort in Las Vegas.</p><p> The portal was also created to support the Irish band&#39;s groundbreaking run of upcoming shows, which will launch off the most state-of-the-art venue, Sphere, the next day (September 29).</p><p> Open daily to the public from September 28, the exhibit borrows its name from the opening track from the 1991 album &#39;Achtung Baby&#39;, and is the nickname for the Zoologischer Garten – an actual Berlin train station, located not far from Hansa Studios where much of the album was recorded.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> U2:UV ACHTUNG BABY LIVE AT SPHERE <a href="https://t.co/tNqEuBgufY">pic.twitter.com/tNqEuBgufY</a></p><p> — U2 (@U2) <a href="https://twitter.com/U2/status/1696720854519107968?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 30, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “Fans can visit the Ultra Violet lounge for music and shopping and the Fly Bar for drinks and more interactive art,” the description of the upcoming portal reads. “Vibee&#39;s VIP package purchasers get priority access and special events at the lounges. Also on the second floor is the Zoo TV Cinema, an intimate theatre curated by The Edge, that will be hosting daily screenings of rare band footage and films.”</p><p> As for the Anton Corbijn Gallery, the exhibit will provide a retrospective look at the photographer&#39;s work, featuring images and footage from across his five decades working alongside the band. The U2 Pop Up Shop, on the other hand, will feature new, never-before-seen merchandise, as well as a collection of limited-edition products made exclusively for this experience.</p><p> Check out remaining tickets for U2&#39;s tour dates <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fu2-tickets%2Fartist%2F736365" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> In other U2 news, earlier this month <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2s-bono-and-the-edge-have-secret-london-wetherspoons-curry-3486732">Bono and The Edge were reported as secretly going to grab a curry from Wetherspoons in London together</a> . The duo made their way to the Central Bar in Shepherd&#39;s Bush to tuck into a bowl of curry from the budget boozer without being spotted.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/u2-announce-zoo-station-immersive-fan-experience-ahead-of-sphere-shows-3491076">U2 announce &#39;Zoo Station&#39; immersive fan experience ahead of Sphere shows</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
